 "html": "<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5792 size-full\" src=\"/media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8007-2.jpg\" alt width=\"720\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8007-2.jpg 720w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8007-2-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8007-2-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8007-2-380x507.jpg 380w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"></p>\n<p>Kom ons maak Naan So so lekker en so so maklik</p>\n<h3>Bestanddele</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>10 ml kitsgis</li>\n<li>5 ml suiker</li>\n<li>125 ml louwater</li>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">750 ml meel</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">2,5 ml sout</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">90 ml olie</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">90 ml ongegeurde jogurt</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">1 eier</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Metode</span></h3>\n<ol>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\"> Sit die kitsgis, suiker en louwater in n koppie en maak toe. Los vir 15 minute</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Met n vurk klits die eier, jogurt en olie saam. Meng met watermengsel</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Sit die meel en sout in n mengbak. Begin die vloeistof stadig inmeng. Knie vir 7 minute. Maak toe en sit in n bak. Laat rys. </span></li>\n<li><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Maak 8 balletjies. Rol uit en braai in n warm pan. Draai om. Smeer met n botter en knoffel mengsel. ( smelt 250 ml botter en 90 ml fyn knoffel in die mikrogolf)</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5791 size-full\" src=\"/media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006.jpg\" alt width=\"960\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006.jpg 960w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006-600x450.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006-300x225.jpg 300w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006-768x576.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006-750x563.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006-500x375.jpg 500w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006-380x285.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006-760x570.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2020/04/IMG_8006-800x600.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"></p>",
